Trusted Advisory


Enquire Here


Reach your goals with our expertise and your business acumen.
At Citi, we believe personal conversations are the best way to get to know your clients and understand how we can support them in achieving their ambitions. That is why our Relationship Manager will take the time to understand your personal situation, financial objectives, and the level of risk you feel comfortable taking to achieve them.

Enquire Here



CITI'S 4-STEP INVESTMENT PROCESS
 With the help of Citi's 4-step advisory process, we can develop well-founded solutions to define and implement your personal investment strategy.


 Throughout the entire process, your dedicated Relationship Manager is supported by a team of Investment Specialists to provide you with the highest quality advice.





STEP 1 - UNDERSTAND

As a Citigold client, you are assigned your own Relationship Manager, whose role is to help you get the most out of your Citigold Relationship. All Citigold Relationship Managers have been handpicked for their investment knowledge and their dedication.
Your Relationship Manager will work with you to create a bespoke portfolio strategy, tailored to your unique circumstances, by assisting you in:

Setting your Goals  Determining the accessible cash and savings required for future expenses—considering children's education, investments, retirement, or personal ambitions.
Defining your goals   Developing an investment strategy to achieve your short, medium and long-term goals that should be the basis on which any financial decisions are made.
Defining your risk profile  Guiding you in establishing your risk profile based on a number of criteria, which will influence your potential returns, as well as the protection of your capital.




STEP 2 - STRATEGIZE

The success of your investment portfolio begins with a selection of sound and well-diversified investments. In order to achieve this, we provide you with a variety of tools and resources to make the most informed decisions.
You will have access to Citi's global investment expertise through our regular market updates and research reports. Your Relationship Manager will also have the support of a team of Investment Specialists to provide comprehensive advice on portfolio management.
Additionally, your Relationship Manager will have the option to tailor asset allocation to your specific needs and investor profile, based on one of the five Citi Model Portfolios. These can also be used as the reference point for periodic evaluations of your investment portfolio.
Citi's Model Portfolios are specifically developed by our investment research teams to provide you with:

A well-diversified portfolio, with an asset composition that is suitable for your financial objectives and risk profile
Asset allocations, which are regularly monitored and, if necessary, revised by Citi's Global Investment Committee to reflect market developments and Citi's house view
Access to high-quality research, developed and published by Citi's global team of analysts located in all major financial centers around the world

Citi Model Portfolios:

Defensive
Income & Growth
Income Oriented
Growth Oriented
Aggressive Growth




Money Markets
												

Fixed Income
												

Equity
												

Global REIT's
												





STEP 3 - IMPLEMENT

At Citi, we offer a wide range of investment products from some of the world's leading asset managers. A team of analysts reviews and selects products from different providers across the globe to offer you a choice of high-quality investment solutions.



STEP 4 - REVIEW

Over time, it is inevitable that both your personal circumstances and market conditions will change. This is why your Relationship Manager will conduct regular portfolio reviews to assess the performance of your investments and help ensure your plans remain firmly on track.





