Investment Products & Platforms


Enquire Here


Reach your goals with numerous ways to invest.
Once you have defined your investment strategy, it's success begins with a sound and well-diversified portfolio of investment products. If you wish to take a more hands-on approach to managing your wealth, our online investment platform provides you with instant access to equities, bonds, mutual funds and ETFs. We also provide unique products like FX Order Watch, so you are always within reach of your goals.

Enquire Here




BROKERAGE SERVICES

Citibank's E-brokerage platform brings you instant access to financial markets across the globe.
International Exchanges supported by this platform are:

Canada (Toronto Stock Exchange, Venture)
France (Euronext Paris Stock Exchange)
Germany (Xetra)
Japan (Tokyo Stock Exchange)
Switzerland (Swiss Stock Exchange, Virt-X)
United Kingdom (London Stock Exchange)
United States (NASDAQ, NYSE, AMEX, NYSE ARCA)




MUTUAL FUNDS

Mutual Funds are professionally managed investment vehicles that pool capital from many investors to invest in multiple stocks, bonds and other securities. Benefits of mutual funds include diversification and professional money management, while offering choice, liquidity and convenience.
To meet your investment needs in various life stages and market conditions, we provide you with different ways to invest in Mutual Funds:

Lump sum investments
Systematic Investment Plans (SIP)




FIXED INCOME SECURITIES

Enjoy a wide selection of bonds issued by reputable organizations worldwide with tenures and currency denominations to suit your investment objectives. Fixed Income securities are ideal for investors who want a regular income and an opportunity for capital appreciation.



STRUCTURED PRODUCTS

We offer a wide selection of structured products, connected with the performance of the underlying stocks, stock market indexes, mutual funds, commodities, or FX.
Every month, our offer will include new proposals for structured notes issued by renowned financial institutions, as well as Certificates of Deposits available under subscription. In addition, you can choose to invest your funds in various currencies under the available Dual Currency Investments.



PREMIUM ACCOUNTS

Premium Accounts are short-term, currency-related investment accounts that provide you with an exciting opportunity to earn potentially higher interest rates as compared to a conventional Time Deposit.
The product is offered across the following currencies:

(USD)
(EUR)
(GBP)
(JPY)
(CHF)
