Insurance


Enquire Here


Reach your goals with complete peace of mind.
Have you considered who depends on you today, whether for financial support or your professional expertise? The chances are that there are more people than you realize. Your income may support a household, covering the mortgage, education costs and many other expenses. You may play a vital role in raising your children and managing the family home. You may be a sole trader, partner or controlling shareholder in a business.
Citibank Insurance Product Suites help our clients guard against various uncertainties, which may arise in their day-to-day lives. We offer:

Enquire Here




PURE LIFE INSURANCE

A Pure Term Life product that offers the easiest and most cost-effective way of providing future financial security for your dependents through life cover, with an option to apply for critical illness and permanent total disability cover.



WHOLE OF LIFE PROTECTION PLANS

An Offshore Whole of Life insurance plan that offers life cover and an option to apply for critical illness and permanent total disability cover, with plan benefits extending up to the age of 95.



SAVINGS PLANS

Investment platforms to structure Savings Plans, Child Education Corpus and Retirement Planning by diversifying across mutual fund portfolios that match your risk appetite.



MOTOR INSURANCE

Motor insurance plays a pivotal role in protecting you, your passengers and your vehicle.



TRAVEL INSURANCE

Insurance against expenses and inconvenience caused by emergency medical conditions, delayed flights, hotel cancellation and baggage delays.



HOME INSURANCE

Home security from any possible adverse eventuality whether you are a house owner, tenant or landlord.



CREDIT PROTECTION

Lifestyle Protection that helps clients provision against Credit Card liabilities in case of death, critical illness and ILOE (Involuntary Loss Of Employment) and offers you other financial benefits for personal use.





