Terms and Conditions
Golf:

If an accompanying guest is not an eligible Citibank Credit Cardmember or Citigold customer, a bestavailable rate will be offered to be paid at the golf course on the date of play, using your Citibank Credit Card. No compulsory paying guest is required
Date and time of play are subject to availability. Confirmed tee time of play may be ± 1 hour of the
									preferred tee time
Advance reservation is requested between 7 to 15 days prior to the date of play
Customer to pay cart fee, caddie fee, insurance and locker fee at normal published rates at the club where
									applicable using a Citibank Credit Card
Golfers must have a valid handicap. Minimum handicap requirement is 28 for men and 36 for ladies
There will be no rain check
The Citibank U.A.E. golf program is not to be regarded as a golf club membership
A club member cannot make a booking directly at the club and transfer the confirmed tee time over to the
									basic Credit Card member
To the fullest extent permissible by law, each participating Citigold customer releases Citibank/the
									respective golf clubs from any claim, loss, damage, cost or expenses (including any claim for legal
									expenses) sustained or incurred by him/her in connection with their participation in the Citibank UAE golf
									program
Citibank Terms and Conditions apply and are subject to change without prior notice. They are available
									upon request and on our website. All offers are made available on a best-effort basis and at the sole
									discretion of Citibank, N.A. Citibank, N.A. makes no warranties and assumes no liability or responsibility
									with respect to the products and services provided by partner(s)/other entity(ies)


Travel & Leisure:

Marhaba Services: A total of 3 passengers traveling with you can avail the free service (1 adult and 2 children)
For every extra passenger traveling with you, you will be required to pay AED 30. To avail the lounge facility, you will be required to pay AED 60 per person
Private Chauffeur: Citigold customers can avail 2 complimentary services per year and Citigold Private Client customers can avail 5 complimentary services per year
Citibank Terms and Conditions apply, are subject to change and are available upon request
Customers should book the service with a lead-time of 48 hours
The client will be charged a flat fee of AED 80 for an additional waiting period in excess of 30 minutes, irrespective of the destination
All offers are made available on a best-effort basis and at the sole discretion of Citibank, N.A. Citibank, N.A. makes no warranties and assumes no liability or responsibility with respect to the products and services provided by the partner(s)/other entity(ies)




